<http://www.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/event/39401AHHBKTRJHJPLGBDBSTVVRJPBTKLC>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "A Court of Crits and Bits";
  schema:description """
	<h2>A devilish curse has befallen the kingdom of Valentine, and only love can break it… or maybe lust?</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\"></span>The Fools’ Guild<span class=\"BoldText\"></span> is oh so pleased to present a spicy sapphic romantasy show in <span class=\"ItalicText\">A Court of Crits & Bits</span>. Six flirty femmes will journey through a tale of deceit and desire, where you decide who gets with who.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Get intimate with the Guild girls and their alluring fantasy world of galas, glamours, and seductions.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This longform narrative improv show will unrobe evil spells and fair maidens alike. Everyone in the royal palace wants a piece of our lovely leading heroine, but among them lurks a villain. Will she fulfil her destiny and find true love, or get caught up in the courtship and lost in the lovemaking along the way?<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Hot. Fantasy. Funny as Hell. <span class=\"ItalicText\">A Court of Crits & Bits</span> is a Valentine's treat you don’t want to miss.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">A Court of Crits & Bits</span> is a Co-Presentation between The Fools' Guild & The Improv Centre.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The Fools’ Guild is a theatre company by and for fantasy lovers, featuring the city’s wittiest, silliest, nerdiest actors. Heroes rise and kingdoms fall in magical remixes of your favorite fiction. These delightful storytellers will take you on an epic quest in a new world every single month!!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Rated: 18A<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please Note: as The Improv Centre is a licensed facility, all minors (persons under the age of 19) must be accompanied by an adult.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Special show – no vouchers allowed.
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-02-15T21:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/files/4c73c6f4-7483-4c09-a194-5058cbb19c70.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/location/603AMBLCJQMLRJDMDQKBNHDKQPPDPCQLJ>;
