<http://www.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/event/51801AMMMQBBLVKCCNBKCBSKVNJHHMGKP>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Duck Duck Moose";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Want to play a game?</h1><span><br/></span>After taking the 2025 Vancouver Fringe Festival by storm, <span class=\"BoldText\">Duck Duck Moose</span> is back for <span class=\"BoldText\">ONE </span><span class=\"BoldText\">NIGHT ONLY!</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Inspired by Netflix’s <span class=\"ItalicText\">Squid Game</span>, this live and fully improvised comedy show throws a fearless cast into a wildly unpredictable world where the stakes are sky-high and the surprises never stop!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Every moment is made up on the spot, with bold moves, ridiculous twists, and nonstop laughs as the story unfolds in ways no one will see coming. And just when you think you’ve got it figured out… think again! It’s all improvised, so anything can happen!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Plus, one lucky audience member will be pulled into the action as the hero of the night! Will they rise to the occasion? Will they make it to the end? There’s only one way to find out!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Whether you’re feeling brave or just want to sit back and enjoy the madness, <span class=\"BoldText\">Duck Duck Moose</span> is a fast-paced, anything-can-happen comedy experience you won’t want to miss!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">“A Top Five Must-See!” (2025 Vancouver Fringe Fest) – The Province<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>“Fast, funny & ferociously bleak!” – Otaku no Culture</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Run time: 90 minutes including intermission.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Rated: 14A<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please Note: as The Improv Centre is a licensed facility, all minors (persons under the age of 19) must be accompanied by an adult.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This show is a guest production. Special Show – Restricted. Vouchers and other discounts do not apply.<span><br/></span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-04-30T21:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/files/8ae944b1-b7fc-4aa7-9dde-2f6801aa890d.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/location/603AMBLCJQMLRJDMDQKBNHDKQPPDPCQLJ>;
  schema:organizer <https://spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/organization/the-improv-centre>;
  schema:url <https://theimprovcentre.ca/shows/>;
  schema:offers _:61bf61df540e4d49aa04255634b383c75401;
  schema:duration "PT90M";
  schema:endDate "2026-04-30T23:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime .

