<http://www.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/event/41201ATDVHVNDPRBLKPLQHLVPNSCNQLLP>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Exploration Blank";
  schema:description """
	<h2>Probing the galaxy, one suggestion at a time!</h2><span><br/></span>See this brand new, limited-run show on Friday & Saturday nights!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>A rotating, rag-tag crew of space explorers is blasting off on an adventure to accomplish… something! Through audience suggestions and a series of improv mini games, they’ll explore a brand-new, dazzling (and dangerous!) galaxy every show. It’s comedy at light-speed!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>From charting undiscovered star systems to being captured by alien civilizations, this out-of-this-world comedy show will excite die-hard sci-fi fans and earth-dwellers new to the genre of all ages!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The only two things you can expect? The unexpected, AND laughter of cosmic proportions!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>These galactic level laughs won't last forever – catch Exploration Blank until June 27th, only at The Improv Centre!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Run time: 90 minutes including intermission.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Rated: PG<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please Note: as The Improv Centre is a licensed facility, all minors (persons under the age of 19) must be accompanied by an adult.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All physical vouchers must now be redeemed via phone or email. Please contact the box office for assistance.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Content Warning</span>: This show contains loud noises, strobing lights, smoke/fog effects, and other stage effects.
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-04-09T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/files/b1d75c4b-0446-4e39-bd57-7fb5c10a63a7.jpeg>;
