<http://www.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/event/57801ABQVHGQHVHPVLHTTSHSNCRVSJPRB>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Fistful of Crime";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Dive headfirst into the seedy underworld of triads, violence, and all the dumplings you can eat!</h1><span><br/></span>In this renowned, one-of-a-kind improv show, you'll experience all the hallmarks of ‘80s and ‘90s Hong Kong gangster cinema, reimagined and remixed on-the-spot by Vancouver's premiere East Asian improv group, <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/fistfulofkicks/\">Fistful of Kicks</a>!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>See a show that's equal parts drama and comedy, exploring characters caught between the criminal world and polite society, stretched thin between their gang allegiances and their family bonds... all created entirely on the spot based on a single word from the audience!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>If you're a seasoned Hong Kong cinema aficionado, or have no idea what any of those words you just read <span class=\"ItalicText\">actually</span> mean, you're going to have a killer time at this show.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Embrace your inner gangster at Fistful of Crime!</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Run time: 90 minutes including intermission.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please Note: as The Improv Centre is a licensed facility, all minors (persons under the age of 19) must be accompanied by an adult.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This show is a guest production. Special Show – Restricted. Vouchers and other discounts do not apply.
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-06-04T21:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/files/891e8144-0648-49c6-a051-c9855dd6f1bf.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/location/603AMBLCJQMLRJDMDQKBNHDKQPPDPCQLJ>;
  schema:organizer <https://spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/organization/the-improv-centre>;
  schema:url <https://theimprovcentre.ca/shows/>;
  schema:offers _:61bf61df540e4d49aa04255634b383c75429;
  schema:duration "PT90M";
  schema:endDate "2026-06-04T23:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime .

