<http://www.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/event/54801ALMQKJGDVBDJQKPLMBMQRRRSMCNM>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Slasher?! Vol. IV";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Slasher is back!</h1><span><br/></span>To celebrate Asian and Pacific Islander Heritage Month, we’ve got a star-studded cast of wonderful Asian performers to showcase their own take on drag and horror. Join us for an evening of chills, spills, and wildly creative thrills as these monsters of drag take you on the ride of a lifetime!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">PERFORMERS</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Bad Shah</span> - @iambad.shah<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Bongganisa</span> - @si.bongganisa<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Carrie Oki Doki</span> - @carrie_oki_doki<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Gaia</span> - @gaiathesinger<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Jalebia Majora</span> - @jalebia.baby<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Mx. Shoop Dumplin'</span> - @dundundumplin<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Papa Pill</span> - @papapilled.drag<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Percy Pegg</span> - @percy.pegg<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Satanix</span> - @satanix.official<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">SKIM</span> - @skimisking<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Vincent Rice</span> - @kingvincentrice<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Yuen Young</span> - @yuen_young<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Hosted by the perpetually tolerated drag king <span class=\"BoldText\">Vincent Rice</span>.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Run time: 60 minutes including intermission<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Rated: Event is 19+ and may contain some sensitive content regarding horror and potentially sexual themes.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">All ticket holders must be 19+ and show ID at the door.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This show is a TIC Guest Production. Special Show – Restricted. Vouchers and other discounts do not apply.
""";
