	<h1>This summer, Vancouver’s longest-running improv show is kicking off with a sporty twist!</h1><span><br/></span>For over 40 years, The Improv Centre has delivered head-to-head Theatresports matches. The players? Two teams of three world-class improvisers. The pitch? A fast-paced slate of high-intensity games. The final score? Decided by you! The crowd's biggest laughs and highest scores decide the winner of the match!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>In Theatresports: Totally Ref’d Up, we’re putting the “sport” back into Theatresports! Hosted by a TIC-appointed referee calling every play, expect a 90-minute, high-octane match-up – filled with red cards, record-breaking scores, and championship-level laughs!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Will it be a shutout or a buzzer-beater finish? There’s only one way to find out.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Get your game on with this limited-time version of Vancouver’s live comedy institution!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Run time: 90 minutes including intermission<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Rated: PG<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please Note: as The Improv Centre is a licensed facility, all minors (persons under the age of 19) must be accompanied by an adult.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All physical vouchers must now be redeemed via phone or email. Please contact the box office for assistance.
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-07-17T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/files/4aece556-4497-40d3-b96a-d43e24aceb94.jpg>;
